355
00:27:09,975 --> 00:27:12,728
You've only known him for a few days,
and you're talking about cohabiting?

356
00:27:12,728 --> 00:27:14,630
It's not cohabiting.

357
00:27:14,630 --> 00:27:17,066
It's just temporary until he moves.

358
00:27:17,066 --> 00:27:19,668
