You two haven't slept together yet.

359
00:27:25,908 --> 00:27:27,325
What?

360
00:27:27,325 --> 00:27:29,044
Did you sleep with him?

361
00:27:33,613 --> 00:27:35,117
<i>Even so,</i>

362
00:27:35,117 --> 00:27:38,053
do you really need

363
00:27:38,053 --> 00:27:41,246
to share everything at the very start?

364
00:27:41,246 --> 00:27:42,006
Is that so?

365
00:27:42,006 --> 00:27:44,727
Weren't you taking things slow?

366
00:27:44,727 --> 00:27:48,197
His bathroom habits, his snoring decibels,

367
00:27:48,197 --> 00:27:50,599
