371
00:27:58,607 --> 00:28:00,275
Right?

372
00:28:05,047 --> 00:28:06,398
Looks like his junior's here.

373
00:28:06,398 --> 00:28:08,183
You can get off.

374
00:28:13,689 --> 00:28:15,759
