378
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:23,532
<i>Her hair's longer than mine,</i>

379
00:28:24,867 --> 00:28:27,101
and she looks slimmer too.

380
00:28:28,567 --> 00:28:32,507
The junior he's crashing with is a woman?

381
00:28:33,210 --> 00:28:36,247
<i>As expected, he's a free spirit
in full storm mode.</i>

382
00:28:36,247 --> 00:28:37,913
Hang up.

383
00:28:47,823 --> 00:28:49,258
Looks like your junior's here.

384
00:28:49,258 --> 00:28:50,427
Yeah.

385
00:28:50,427 --> 00:28:52,928
Just went back up for the last box.

386
00:28:53,455 --> 00:28:55,898
You must be really close.

387
00:28:55,898 --> 00:28:57,575
My closest junior.

388
00:28:57,575 --> 00:28:59,401
We've seen it all,

389
00:29:00,202 --> 00:29:01,337
good and bad.

390
00:29:01,337 --> 00:29:02,950
Do Hyun.

391
00:29:03,839 --> 00:29:05,432
Yes.

392
00:29:06,475 --> 00:29:08,143
So...

393
00:29:08,717 --> 00:29:09,712
Well...

394
00:29:09,712 --> 00:29:11,968
Here's your coffee.

395
00:29:11,968 --> 00:29:13,716
Thank you.

396
00:29:13,716 --> 00:29:15,316
Wait.

397
00:29:22,042 --> 00:29:24,092
Want to stay at my place?

398
00:29:26,724 --> 00:29:28,430
Uh...

399
00:29:28,430 --> 00:29:30,030
Well...

400
00:29:31,642 --> 00:29:33,502
So...

401
00:29:33,502 --> 00:29:35,767
It's close for moving,

402
00:29:35,767 --> 00:29:37,840
the place is spacious,

403
00:29:37,840 --> 00:29:39,443
and, um...

404
00:29:39,443 --> 00:29:41,577
