409
00:29:54,391 --> 00:29:56,191
Woo Jung Hoon.

410
00:30:03,822 --> 00:30:04,833
Say hi.

411
00:30:04,833 --> 00:30:06,637
This is Seo Jun Kyung.

412
00:30:06,637 --> 00:30:08,037
My girlfriend.

413
00:30:08,037 --> 00:30:09,907
Oh,

414
00:30:09,907 --> 00:30:11,907
