419
00:30:31,595 --> 00:30:35,730
I'm not that Hollywood.

420
00:30:36,834 --> 00:30:38,133
It's just...

421
00:30:38,133 --> 00:30:41,303
No, I mean... his hair looks so silky,

422
00:30:41,303 --> 00:30:44,839
and his legs are so slim.

423
00:30:47,601 --> 00:30:50,201
I should treat him to a meal sometime.

424
00:30:50,201 --> 00:30:52,673
We should eat too.

425
00:30:53,740 --> 00:30:55,701
Since it's moving day,

426
00:30:55,701 --> 00:30:57,920
