434
00:31:27,483 --> 00:31:29,825
Then, we won't need oxytocin.

435
00:31:29,825 --> 00:31:31,519
I'll head over now.

436
00:31:34,758 --> 00:31:36,345
Hey, Sol.

437
00:31:36,345 --> 00:31:38,245
You said four people, right?

438
00:31:38,245 --> 00:31:39,805
Five?

439
00:31:39,805 --> 00:31:42,499
That's fine. Totally fine.

440
00:31:42,499 --> 00:31:44,400
I've already taken care of everything,

441
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:46,668
so just show up.

442
00:31:58,033 --> 00:31:59,714
Okay.

443
00:32:42,391 --> 00:32:44,726
