452
00:33:16,156 --> 00:33:20,061
Luckily, someone at the lobby had a sewing kit.

453
00:33:20,929 --> 00:33:22,616
You must be very handy.

454
00:33:22,616 --> 00:33:24,006
Not really.

455
00:33:24,006 --> 00:33:25,936
I just made sure

456
00:33:25,936 --> 00:33:28,103
