457
00:33:32,441 --> 00:33:35,043
What are you doing for dinner?

458
00:33:36,723 --> 00:33:38,377
I'm just going to grab
something quick in my room.

459
00:33:38,377 --> 00:33:41,410
Don't rush a meal. Every meal matters.

460
00:33:41,410 --> 00:33:43,971
Try the Italian place in the Ocean Wing.

461
00:33:43,971 --> 00:33:45,954
It's pretty solid.

462
00:33:48,524 --> 00:33:51,650
Want to grab dinner together?

463
00:33:51,650 --> 00:33:55,096
