464
00:34:29,066 --> 00:34:31,299
I guess I'm just not great at this.

465
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,868
I saw you booked

466
00:35:03,868 --> 00:35:06,935
the yacht tour for tomorrow.

467
00:35:08,339 --> 00:35:09,940
Yes.

468
00:35:14,376 --> 00:35:17,478
I signed up because my wife would've loved it.

469
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:20,848
But recently,

470
00:35:22,517 --> 00:35:24,886
