471
00:35:25,634 --> 00:35:27,230
Oh...

472
00:35:28,225 --> 00:35:30,491
I wished we could've come together,

473
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:33,061
but it's too late now.

474
00:35:35,840 --> 00:35:37,699
You still came.

475
00:35:41,406 --> 00:35:43,538
That matters.

476
00:35:48,810 --> 00:35:50,980
- Happy birthday to you.
- Happy birthday to you.

477
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:53,081
- Happy birthday to you.
- Happy birthday to you.

478
00:35:53,081 --> 00:35:57,885
- Happy birthday to my dear Sol.
- Happy birthday to my dear Sol.

