00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:29,183
Just a moment.

482
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,833
What are you doing?

483
00:36:43,833 --> 00:36:46,535
Please go outside.

484
00:36:46,535 --> 00:36:48,169
It's okay. Let's step out.

485
00:36:49,934 --> 00:36:51,806
