496
00:37:49,498 --> 00:37:52,467
I'm a person of faith.

497
00:37:53,304 --> 00:37:54,434
Then

498
00:37:54,434 --> 00:37:56,504
I suppose there's nothing to worry about.

499
00:37:59,007 --> 00:38:01,753
