500
00:38:01,753 --> 00:38:02,644
Pardon?

501
00:38:02,644 --> 00:38:04,602
I mean people who come here to end it all.

502
00:38:05,514 --> 00:38:07,551
Yes, there was a case quite a while back.

503
00:38:07,551 --> 00:38:09,851
On the Camino de Santiago.

504
00:38:11,253 --> 00:38:13,253
I really enjoyed today.

505
00:38:13,253 --> 00:38:15,456
Same here.

506
00:38:38,242 --> 00:38:40,181
<i>Call me when you wrap up.</i>

507
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,767
It's me.

508
00:38:52,767 --> 00:38:54,830
I'm all done now.

509
00:38:54,830 --> 00:38:56,464
That took ages.

510
00:38:56,464 --> 00:38:58,700
That kid really owes his mom everything.

511
00:38:58,700 --> 00:39:01,601
