512
00:39:01,601 --> 00:39:04,901
I'm wiped out and starving too.

513
00:39:04,901 --> 00:39:05,874
Get here soon.

514
00:39:05,874 --> 00:39:08,167
I didn't eat,

515
00:39:08,167 --> 00:39:09,636
waiting to eat with you.

516
00:39:09,636 --> 00:39:11,415
Still?

517
00:39:11,415 --> 00:39:13,514
You should've gone ahead.

518
00:39:14,975 --> 00:39:17,752
