519
00:39:18,355 --> 00:39:21,592
How about those noodles
we missed out on earlier?

520
00:39:21,592 --> 00:39:22,860
Sounds good.

521
00:39:22,860 --> 00:39:24,275
Hurry over.

522
00:39:24,275 --> 00:39:25,862
Okay.

523
00:39:31,766 --> 00:39:33,801
[The Man Next Door]

524
00:39:39,908 --> 00:39:43,611
